metadata.description: Catalyst Prime has begun! Daniel DosSantos is a young man living at the speed of life. After gaining powers from exposure to an extraterrestrial object, DosSantos became the rapid action superhero called Accell, the first of a new public kind of self-appointed crime fighter. Unfortunately, there are consequences to moving faster than sound. Accell is about to learn that danger exists on the flipside of having superpowers and will have to grow up quickly to survive.
metadata.name: Accell
